client for echo service

Usage howto
==================
1, Change echo_client.xml. 
  Setup the library path. 
  Setup the endpoint of the remote service.
  Setup the credential which will be used by tls.
  Setup the WS-Security usernametoken information. You just need to setup the username and password which you would use
      to access this service, if the service require usenametoken authentication.
2, Run "arcecho echo_client.xml"; IF succeed, you can get response like: [ echo_client.xml ] 
 
